.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \fB\-e RECIPE_TEXT\fP, \fB\-\-execute RECIPE_TEXT\fP
Use to execute a resource using a string.
.TP
.B \fB\-l LEVEL\fP, \fB\-\-log_level LEVEL\fP
